What is ENACTUS?

Enactus is a global network that inspires young people to use entrepreneurship to solve social and economic challenges. Enactus Maroc, founded in 2003, is part of this network and offers students the opportunity to carry out innovative projects with a direct impact on their community.

Objectives of Enactus FSBM

  • 🎓 Encourage student engagement
  • 🚀 Develop a new generation of entrepreneurial leaders
  • 🌍 Enable companies to have a strong social impact
  • 🧩 Address key social challenges
